	<description>
		Flogging Dolly is an action oriented endless runner with a novel control mechanism.
		The player controls a sheep by slapping it with a finger (in a similar way as slicing fruit in fruit slicing games).
		To maintain speed player must hit speed boosters. In order not to get eaten by a monster.
	</description>

